  "Description": {
    "English": "This odd collection of wires pulses with a faint, almost organic energy. It seems to remember the whole from which it was parted...<br><br>Process in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span> to generate 'edible' products.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这些奇怪的电线上闪着微弱而几乎是有机的能量。它似乎还记得自己被分离的母体......<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>中处理以产生“可食用”的产品。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "奇怪的一團電線，可以感受到淡淡的能量脈衝，彷彿是有機的。這團電線似乎記得自己是從哪裡被拔掉的......<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>中加工即可製造出「可食用」的產品。"
  },
